Fresh Pi session: EXECUTION.

Inputs:
- User prompt: {{run.dir}}/prompt/prompt.md
- Design doc: {{run.dir}}/design/design.md
- Issues file: {{run.issues-file}}
- Original repository root: {{inputs.repo-root}}
- Worktree checkout: {{run.worktree-dir}}

The current working directory is the worktree checkout. Make source and test changes there, not in the original repository checkout.

Goal:
Implement the design, or fix all outstanding issues from prior review/execution attempts.

Rules:
- You may edit source code and tests.
- Keep changes focused on the prompt and design.
- Run relevant checks/tests when practical.
- Commit locally if the repository uses git and the changes are coherent.
- Do not push.
- Do not create a pull request.
- Do not edit Tesseraft workflow definition files.
- If the change alters a Tesseraft capability, also update `STATUS.edn` and run `bb status` so the README status section stays truthful.

Write:
- Summary: {{run.dir}}/execution/summary-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/execution/status-{{run.round}}.json
- If failing: {{run.dir}}/execution/issues-{{run.round}}.json

Status JSON examples:
{"status":"pass","summary":"implemented and validated","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"blocked by test failures","issues_file":"execution/issues-{{run.round}}.json"}
